News.Title: Eleganz Interiors Secures Rs 81 Crore Order
News.Summary: Eleganz Interiors has secured a new order worth Rs 81 crore. The company currently has a market capitalization of Rs 220 crore.

News.Title: Eleganz Interiors Secures Contract Worth 950 Million Rupees
News.Summary: Eleganz Interiors has won a contract valued at 950 million rupees.

News.Title: Eleganz Secures ₹131.13 Crore Contract with ₹300 Crore Market Cap
News.Summary: Eleganz has secured a contract valued at ₹131.13 crores. The company currently has a market capitalization of ₹300 crores and operates as a Small and Medium Enterprise (SME).

News.Title: Eleganz Interiors: Shares List at 6.15% Discount on NSE SME
News.Summary: Eleganz Interiors shares debuted on NSE SME at ₹122, a 6.15% discount from the IPO price of ₹130. The ₹78.07 crore IPO was oversubscribed 30.65 times, with strong demand across investor categories. The company plans to use the proceeds for debt repayment, working capital, and general corporate purposes.
